title: Slowing a Nation-Maltese Speed Limits
description:
Can you imagine being restricted to driving on a highway at 60km/h (37miles/h) and being fined for going over that limit? The Maltese authorities have discovered a new method of how to tax drivers. 

This pdf/mp3 article lists the various reasons given from imposing this limit together with a counter comments.

You will also find information on how you can help put a stop to this injustice.
